Text.SourceString: Thank Hooman for freeing <NPCName>Grog</>.
Text.LocalizedString: Thank Hooman for freeing <NPCName>Grog</>.

Text.SourceString: You have large land. Best for farming. Plants give life to Earth.//Land die if you don't farm. It get hard, crusty and sad.
Text.LocalizedString: You have large land. Best for farming. Plants give life to Earth.//Land die if you don't farm. It get hard, crusty and sad.

Text.SourceString: Giants plant and nurture earth.//Flowers and trees feed Giants and earth.
Text.LocalizedString: Giants plant and nurture earth.//Flowers and trees feed Giants and earth.

Text.SourceString: We plant trees...flowers in happy mood so earth happy too.
Text.LocalizedString: We plant trees...flowers in happy mood so earth happy too.

Text.SourceString: Um, <NPCName>Grog</> want to ask. Can Hooman dance?
Text.LocalizedString: Um, <NPCName>Grog</> want to ask. Can Hooman dance?

Text.SourceString: N-no, <NPCName>Grog</> just want to ask!
Text.LocalizedString: N-no, <NPCName>Grog</> just want to ask!

Text.SourceString: Yes, same with <NPCName>Grog</>.//Eh, <NPCName>Grog</> said nothing!
Text.LocalizedString: Yes, same with <NPCName>Grog</>.//Eh, <NPCName>Grog</> said nothing!

Special.SourceString: No, I have two left feet!
Special.LocalizedString: No, I have two left feet!

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Grog</> can make tool powerful.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Grog</> can make tool powerful.

Text.SourceString: But Giants together will make tool much more powerful.//Giants have share magic.
Text.LocalizedString: But Giants together will make tool much more powerful.//Giants have share magic.

Text.SourceString: Practice is hard. Magic is hard.//<NPCName>Grog</> need to nap.
Text.LocalizedString: Practice is hard. Magic is hard.//<NPCName>Grog</> need to nap.

Text.SourceString: It is nice that <NPCName>Grog</> can work the Earth again.//Thank you Hooman. I wish <NPCName>Goddess</> gift you good things only.
Text.LocalizedString: It is nice that <NPCName>Grog</> can work the Earth again.//Thank you Hooman. I wish <NPCName>Goddess</> gift you good things only.

Text.SourceString: Goomgoom Hooman.//Hooman need help from <NPCName>Grog</>? <NPCName>Grog</> can help with hooman tools.
Text.LocalizedString: Goomgoom Hooman.//Hooman need help from <NPCName>Grog</>? <NPCName>Grog</> can help with hooman tools.

Text.SourceString: Forest full of magic. A safe place for Giants, animals and Hooman.//Giants safe to be Giants here. <NPCName>Goddess</> keep Giants safe.
Text.LocalizedString: Forest full of magic. A safe place for Giants, animals and Hooman.//Giants safe to be Giants here. <NPCName>Goddess</> keep Giants safe.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Groo</> like to taste hooman food.//I like hooman food too but spikey fruit still favorite.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Groo</> like to taste hooman food.//I like hooman food too but spikey fruit still favorite.

Text.SourceString: You can plant spikey fruit now.//Sprouting Season is spikey fruit season.
Text.LocalizedString: You can plant spikey fruit now.//Sprouting Season is spikey fruit season.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Grog</> think <NPCName>Chieftain</> loney...goom...LONELY, not loney.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Grog</> think <NPCName>Chieftain</> loney...goom...LONELY, not loney.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Grog</> and other Giants gone for so long...
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Grog</> and other Giants gone for so long...

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Grog</> feels good to be back in village. Now <NPCName>Grog</> can help <NPCName>Chieftain</> again with taking care island.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Grog</> feels good to be back in village. Now <NPCName>Grog</> can help <NPCName>Chieftain</> again with taking care island.

Text.SourceString: Others usually not look for <NPCName>Grog</>. But <NPCName>Grog</> happy that Hooman want to see <NPCName>Grog</>.
Text.LocalizedString: Others usually not look for <NPCName>Grog</>. But <NPCName>Grog</> happy that Hooman want to see <NPCName>Grog</>.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Grog</> has many stuff from the Hooman vilage. <NPCName>Grog</> favorite is the hat.//Very nice, but very small for <NPCName>Grog</> head.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Grog</> has many stuff from the Hooman vilage. <NPCName>Grog</> favorite is the hat.//Very nice, but very small for <NPCName>Grog</> head.

Text.SourceString: Giants take care of island together.//Together with Hooman too from many moons ago.
Text.LocalizedString: Giants take care of island together.//Together with Hooman too from many moons ago.

Text.SourceString: This Giant Village. This island is Giants home.//Hooman home too.
Text.LocalizedString: This Giant Village. This island is Giants home.//Hooman home too.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Grog</> happy to see Hooman farm. Taking care of Earth.//More plants in island, more Giants, animals and Hooman are fed.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Grog</> happy to see Hooman farm. Taking care of Earth.//More plants in island, more Giants, animals and Hooman are fed.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Grog</> house better than cavern. Very soft and warm.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Grog</> house better than cavern. Very soft and warm.

Text.SourceString: Hooman home soft or no?
Text.LocalizedString: Hooman home soft or no?

Text.SourceString: Forest is pretty. Hooman farm pretty too?//Many plants and animals or no?
Text.LocalizedString: Forest is pretty. Hooman farm pretty too?//Many plants and animals or no?

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Grog</> can not enchant tools here...//<NPCName>Grog</> need to go outside to enchant tools.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Grog</> can not enchant tools here...//<NPCName>Grog</> need to go outside to enchant tools.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Grog</> not sure <NPCName>Grog</> want to go outside today...//Nap time.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Grog</> not sure <NPCName>Grog</> want to go outside today...//Nap time.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Grog</> like rain. Rain feed Earth with goodness and energy.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Grog</> like rain. Rain feed Earth with goodness and energy.

Text.SourceString: Rain brings life to forest and Earth.
Text.LocalizedString: Rain brings life to forest and Earth.

Text.SourceString: Forest get nice drink today.//Thank you <NPCName>Goddess</>.
Text.LocalizedString: Forest get nice drink today.//Thank you <NPCName>Goddess</>.

Text.SourceString: Good day today, Hooman. <NPCName>Grog</> will train magic.
Text.LocalizedString: Good day today, Hooman. <NPCName>Grog</> will train magic.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Grog</> grateful for sun today.//Important to make plants grow.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Grog</> grateful for sun today.//Important to make plants grow.

Text.SourceString: Nice day for training. <NPCName>Grog</> can throw rocks no problem.//Goomgom!
Text.LocalizedString: Nice day for training. <NPCName>Grog</> can throw rocks no problem.//Goomgom!

Text.SourceString: Today have good vibe. The sun, warm and the Earth, happy.//If Earth happy, <NPCName>Grog</> happy.
Text.LocalizedString: Today have good vibe. The sun, warm and the Earth, happy.//If Earth happy, <NPCName>Grog</> happy.

Text.SourceString: Ice Season now. Everything white and cold.//Earth is sleeping. <NPCName>Grog</> should too.
Text.LocalizedString: Ice Season now. Everything white and cold.//Earth is sleeping. <NPCName>Grog</> should too.

Text.SourceString: Hard to see in snow. Grateful for Giant stone signs in forest.//Snow burry path. <NPCName>Grog</> get confused and lost.
Text.LocalizedString: Hard to see in snow. Grateful for Giant stone signs in forest.//Snow burry path. <NPCName>Grog</> get confused and lost.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Grog</> get lost and stuck in Hooman Village for long.//<NPCName>Grog</> eat same red berry everyday.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Grog</> get lost and stuck in Hooman Village for long.//<NPCName>Grog</> eat same red berry everyday.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Grog</> sleep at new friend home.//Furry friend have large home near berry patch.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Grog</> sleep at new friend home.//Furry friend have large home near berry patch.

Text.SourceString: Earth is cold now. <NPCName>Grog</> can feel in body.//But very pretty... <NPCName>Grog</> is happy to see Earth pretty.
Text.LocalizedString: Earth is cold now. <NPCName>Grog</> can feel in body.//But very pretty... <NPCName>Grog</> is happy to see Earth pretty.

Text.SourceString: The wind feel nice. Sprouting Season is <NPCName>Grog</> favorite.//All season is <NPCName>Grog</> favorite!
Text.LocalizedString: The wind feel nice. Sprouting Season is <NPCName>Grog</> favorite.//All season is <NPCName>Grog</> favorite!

Text.SourceString: The wind feel nice.//Falling Season is <NPCName>Grog</> favorite.
Text.LocalizedString: The wind feel nice.//Falling Season is <NPCName>Grog</> favorite.

Text.SourceString: The snow feel nice.//Ice Season is <NPCName>Grog</> favorite.
Text.LocalizedString: The snow feel nice.//Ice Season is <NPCName>Grog</> favorite.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Grog</> need to go to forest and find fruits.//Giants like fruits. You eat fruits too or no? Ancient hooman like fruits like Giants.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Grog</> need to go to forest and find fruits.//Giants like fruits. You eat fruits too or no? Ancient hooman like fruits like Giants.

Text.SourceString: Hooman likes to gather food and eat together by the lake, yes?//Nice, Giants like to do that at village too.
Text.LocalizedString: Hooman likes to gather food and eat together by the lake, yes?//Nice, Giants like to do that at village too.

Text.SourceString: Hooman and Giants are same...even when Hooman and <NPCName>Grog</> look different.
Text.LocalizedString: Hooman and Giants are same...even when Hooman and <NPCName>Grog</> look different.

Text.SourceString: Sprouting Season but still no spikey fruits in forest. Sad.
Text.LocalizedString: Sprouting Season but still no spikey fruits in forest. Sad.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Grog</> and <NPCName>Groo</> got many spikey fruits yesterday at forest.//Giants happy! Thank you <NPCName>Goddess</>!
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Grog</> and <NPCName>Groo</> got many spikey fruits yesterday at forest.//Giants happy! Thank you <NPCName>Goddess</>!

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Grog</> can feel the wind getting colder. Falling Season is almost over.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Grog</> can feel the wind getting colder. Falling Season is almost over.

Text.SourceString: Many plants are sprouting in forest...//<NPCName>Grog</> can feel Earth is very happy.
Text.LocalizedString: Many plants are sprouting in forest...//<NPCName>Grog</> can feel Earth is very happy.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Grog</> have many friends in forest. Especially after sundown.//<NPCName>Grog</> friends come out when all is dark.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Grog</> have many friends in forest. Especially after sundown.//<NPCName>Grog</> friends come out when all is dark.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Grog</> told friends in forest, don't take fruits from Hooman.//But some friends are naughty like <NPCName>Gong</> and don't listen.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Grog</> told friends in forest, don't take fruits from Hooman.//But some friends are naughty like <NPCName>Gong</> and don't listen.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Chieftain</> say no perfect friends.//Not even <NPCName>Grog</> is perfect. So even naughty, <NPCName>Grog</> still love naughty friends.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Chieftain</> say no perfect friends.//Not even <NPCName>Grog</> is perfect. So even naughty, <NPCName>Grog</> still love naughty friends.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Grog</> looking forward to Sprouting Season.//Spikey fruits everywhere in Sprouting Season.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Grog</> looking forward to Sprouting Season.//Spikey fruits everywhere in Sprouting Season.
